5)	ORPHANAGE
Project ASHRA - Empowering Futures (AFLF-Free Education Shelter) 

Welcome to Project “AASHRA” The (AFLF)"Ashray For Life Foundation," also recognized as "Ashray Ka Aashra from Malad," is situated in Malad. AFLF organization serves as a haven of free education for underprivileged children. With a dedicated team known as AFLF, the foundation comes together to address the needs of these children, ensuring that they receive the support they require. As a part of their mission, the foundation distributes education kits to these young minds, paving the way for a promising and luminous future. At Project Aashra, we believe in the transformative power of education. Our mission is to provide free education and support to underprivileged and orphaned children. Every child deserves the opportunity to learn, grow, and build a brighter future, and we are committed to making this a reality.

*Our Commitment:*

 *Free Education:* We offer free education to all children in the Ashra shelter, ensuring that financial constraints do not hinder their access to quality learning.

*School Supplies:* We provide school bags and stationery to all the children, equipping them with the tools they need to excel in their studies.We envision a world where every child has the chance to break free from the cycle of poverty through education. By investing in the education of underprivileged and orphaned children, we are sowing the seeds for a more equitable and hopeful future.

You can be a part of this transformative journey by supporting Project Ashra. Whether through donations, volunteering, or spreading the word about our mission, together, we can empower these young minds to reach their full potential.

Join us in making a difference and shaping a brighter tomorrow for these children. Together, we can light up their path to a better future. 


6)	MEDICAL
Project LIFE-LINE - Saving Lives

Welcome to Project “LIFE-LINE” At AFLF, we firmly believe that every heartbeat counts, especially when it belongs to a child or a person in desperate need of life-saving surgery. Project Lifeline is our unwavering commitment to providing a lifeline of hope to the poorest and most vulnerable among us.

*Our Mission:*

*Saving Children's Lives:* We understand that for many little hearts, access to vital surgeries is a matter of survival. Project Lifeline steps in as their lifeline, ensuring that no child faces the threat of critical illness due to financial limitations.

*Critical Surgery Support:* We take on the cases of individuals, especially children, who require complex and costly surgeries but lack the means to pay for them. Through dedicated fundraising efforts, we mobilize the resources required to grant them a second chance at life.

*Compassionate Care:* Project Lifeline embodies the spirit of compassion and unwavering solidarity. We firmly believe in the power of communities coming together to create miracles, one surgery at a time.

*Join Our Lifesaving Mission:* You can be a part of this vital mission by contributing to Project Lifeline. Your support, whether through donations or by spreading the word about our cause, can help us continue saving lives and offering hope to those who need it the most.

*One Surgery, One Life Saved:* Project Lifeline is a testament to the extraordinary impact that collective compassion can achieve. It's not just about surgeries; it's about giving children and individuals the precious gift of life itself. Join AFLF in this noble humanitarian effort to save lives and create a brighter, healthier future for all.


7)	OLD-AGE HOME 
*Project  - Empowering Elder Lives with Dignity*

Welcome to Project “SAHARA” At AFLF, we are dedicated to a cause that transcends age, but centers on the invaluable wisdom and experience of our elderly population. We envision a society where our seniors have the right to an active, healthy, and dignified life, regardless of their circumstances.

*Our Mission:*

*Advocating for the Elderly:* In a country with a projected 138 million elderly individuals, AFLF is their voice. We champion their concerns and rights, working tirelessly to ensure that they lead secure, joyful, and dignified lives.

*Supporting Old-Age Homes:* We understand that for some, old-age homes are their haven. We provide essential support in the form of food grains, regular visits, and quality time spent, making their days brighter and more meaningful.

*Celebrating Life's Moments:* Our commitment goes beyond basic support. We celebrate the special occasions of our elderly friends, like birthdays and festivals, bringing smiles, joy, and a sense of belonging to their lives.

*Join Our Cause:* You too can become a part of our mission to empower and uplift the lives of disadvantaged older persons. Whether through donations, volunteering, or simply spreading awareness about our cause, together, we can ensure that our seniors live their golden years with the dignity and respect they deserve.
